Here's the PlantUML sequence diagram for the Bee Green application's control flow:

```plantuml
@startuml JessNah_BeeGreen

actor User
participant "Chrome Extension" as Extension
participant "Client Website (React)" as Client
participant "Server (LoopBack 4)" as Server
participant "E-commerce Site" as Ecom

User -> Extension: Activates extension while shopping
Extension -> Ecom: Injects content script
Ecom --> Extension: Returns cart data
Extension -> Extension: Analyzes cart data
Extension -> Server: Requests sustainability scores
Server -> Server: Calculates scores
Server --> Extension: Returns scores + alternatives
Extension -> User: Displays sustainability info

User -> Client: Visits website
Client -> Server: Requests user data
Server --> Client: Returns dashboard data
Client -> User: Displays dashboard

User -> Client: Submits contribution
Client -> Server: Posts contribution data
Server -> Server: Processes and stores data
Server --> Client: Confirms receipt
Client -> User: Shows confirmation

@enduml
```